author: bago
msg: Updated AbstractRemoteDeliveryTest to better check results in testMulti (related to JAMES-850).

Some of the test had a simulation of a one-on-two failing server. The expected result was a success delivery because we do multiple attempts but this was not predictable when we run mutliple deliveries.
Introduced an "unknown" expected result so that for some of them we accept both a SENT or a FAILURE, but we at least check we had a delivery attempt (not IDLE).
